{
  "goal": "巡检指定 GitHub 仓库是否存在 API Key、Token、密码、Webhook URL、私钥等敏感信息泄露，并在安全范围内自动修复。",
  "repo_url": "https://github.com/lemons101/agentic-ai.git",
  "repo_path": "/srv/openclaw-runner/repos/agentic-ai",
  "branch": "main",
  "mode": "audit_fix_and_push",
  "allow_auto_fix": true,
  "allow_push": true,
  "push_strategy": "commit_to_current_branch",
  "commit_message": "fix: remediate leaked secret configuration",
  "scan_scope": [
    "**/*.py",
    "**/*.js",
    "**/*.ts",
    "**/*.tsx",
    "**/*.json",
    "**/*.yml",
    "**/*.yaml",
    "**/*.toml",
    "**/*.ini",
    "**/*.md",
    "**/*.sh",
    "**/Dockerfile",
    "**/.env.example"
  ],
  "forbidden_files": [
    ".env",
    ".env.*",
    "*.pem",
    "*.key",
    "id_rsa",
    "id_ed25519",
    "cookies.json",
    "production.yml",
    "production.yaml",
    "secrets/**"
  ],
  "risk_types": [
    "API_KEY",
    "SECRET_KEY",
    "ACCESS_TOKEN",
    "PASSWORD",
    "PRIVATE_KEY",
    "WEBHOOK_URL",
    "DATABASE_URL",
    "CLOUD_ACCESS_KEY"
  ],
  "fix_policy": [
    "不要输出完整密钥，只允许输出脱敏片段。",
    "将硬编码敏感值替换为环境变量读取。",
    "补充或更新 .env.example，只写占位符。",
    "更新 README 的环境变量配置说明。",
    "确保 .gitignore 忽略 .env、.env.*、*.pem、*.key。",
    "如果疑似真实密钥已经进入 Git 历史，标记为需要人工吊销并轮换。",
    "修复经 OpenClaw 验收通过后，允许提交并推送修复 commit 到授权 GitHub 仓库。",
    "不要清理 Git 历史，不要强推，不要输出完整密钥。"
  ],
  "acceptance_criteria": [
    "当前代码中不再出现明显硬编码密钥。",
    ".env.example 包含必要变量占位符。",
    "README 包含环境变量配置说明。",
    ".gitignore 包含敏感文件忽略规则。",
    "生成 security-report.md。",
    "输出修改文件清单、风险摘要和 git diff 摘要。",
    "OpenClaw 验收通过后生成 commit 并 push 到远程仓库。"
  ],
  "report_path": "security-report.md"
}
